description: Alelion Energy Systems AB engages in the development, manufacture, and sale of industrial energy storage systems based on lithium-ion technology. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 38 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-06-21. The firm designs and optimizes complete energy control systems. The firm offers electronics hardware and power systems, including battery management systems, battery packs and complete batteries, energy storage and control systems, battery supervision and monitoring products, and control software with service developer kits.
